		<item>
		<title>Who won the horse race? Bofa. Bofa Deez Nutz.</title>
		<link>https://boingboing.net/2018/06/05/who-won-the-horse-race-bofa.html</link>
		<comments>https://boingboing.net/2018/06/05/who-won-the-horse-race-bofa.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 05 Jun 2018 17:27:11 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[David Pescovitz]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Post]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Video]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Funny]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[got eeem]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[horse racing]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[horses]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[sports]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://boingboing.net/?p=602823</guid>



		<description><![CDATA[<img width="480" height="360" src="https://i2.wp.com/media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/0-2.jpg?fit=480%2C360&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/0-2.jpg?w=480&amp;ssl=1 480w, https://i2.wp.com/media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/0-2.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" /> <p> <P>
A horse named <a href="http://www.equibase.com/profiles/Results.cfm?type=Horse&refno=10057981&registry=Q&rbt=QH">Bofa Deez Nutz</a> won its first victory on Friday at Oklahoma City's Remington Park. You'll note that the race caller is a master at his craft. <P>
Meanwhile, as the horse crossed the finish line, its owner could be heard exclaiming "GOT EEEEM!" (In my imagination anyway.)
<P>
<em>(Thanks, <a href="https://twitter.com/deanputney">Dean Putney</a>!)</em>
<P>]]></description>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="480" height="360" src="https://i2.wp.com/media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/0-2.jpg?fit=480%2C360&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/0-2.jpg?w=480&amp;ssl=1 480w, https://i2.wp.com/media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/0-2.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" /> <p> <P>
A horse named <a href="http://www.equibase.com/profiles/Results.cfm?type=Horse&refno=10057981&registry=Q&rbt=QH">Bofa Deez Nutz</a> won its first victory on Friday at Oklahoma City's Remington Park. You'll note that the race caller is a master at his craft. <P>
Meanwhile, as the horse crossed the finish line, its owner could be heard exclaiming "GOT EEEEM!" (In my imagination anyway.)
<P>
<em>(Thanks, <a href="https://twitter.com/deanputney">Dean Putney</a>!)</em>
<P>]]></content:encoded>


