Intel and Chinese tech firm Ehang UAV have been locked in a battle over the world record for largest drone lightshow, and Ehang recently took the lead with <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4mHDDG3FCjs">1,374 drones as voxels</a>.
<p>
